In kyocera Net Viewer's main interface, right-click on the where the module will be installed;

In the options menu that will open, go to Advanced and click Manage Apps...;

In the window, select Install App and check enable app after installation option;

On the next screen, click Search;

In the window that opens, find the .pkg and click Open;

Click Finish to start installation on the device;

If the solution is installed correctly, the Result field will display a success message;

Click Close.

In kyocera Net Viewer's main interface, right-click on the where the solution will be uninstalled;

In the options menu that will open, go to Advanced and click Manage Apps...;

In the window, select Uninstall application;

On the next screen, select Specify package installed on the device;

In the window that opens, the source will be shown, if it is correct click Next;

All applications installed on the will be listed, select the desired one and click Next;

Click Finish to start uninstalling the device;

If the solution is uninstalled correctly, the Result field will display a success message;

Click Close.
